O2Jam To Osu¶

class reamber.algorithms.convert.O2JToOsu.O2JToOsu¶

Bases: object

static convert(o2j: reamber.o2jam.O2JMapSetObj.O2JMapSetObj) → List[reamber.osu.OsuMapObj.OsuMapObj]¶

Converts a Mapset to multiple Osu maps

Note that a mapset contains maps, so a list would be expected. O2JMap conversion is not possible due to lack of O2JMapset Metadata

Parameters

o2j – O2Jam Mapset

Returns

List of Osu Maps
